flow.description: A start flow created along with the agent

variants.text: Hello! I’m Breezy, the AI Assistant for Screens by Kaidan. I can help you book an appointment, give you a quick quote, check pricing, or answer any questions about our services. What can I help you with today?
Great! You can book an appointment anytime using our online calendar. Click below to get started!
Let me check the next available openings for you!
Our next available appointments are usually within 2–3 days. You can view exact times and book directly here:
Sure! For basic prices just ask for the pricelist or tell me what you specifically need. For a detailed quote, click below and fill out our request form.
No problem! You can call or text us at 760-248-8000, or email info@screensbykaidan.com. We're here to help!
You can access your customer portal below to check, change or reschedule your appointments or to view estimates.
Hang tight while I check our real-time availability!

parts.text: I need to schedule a visit
Can I book an appointment with you?
I'd like to make an appointment

How soon can you come out?

meta.description: "Yes" response to the question, "Does this time work, or would you like to see more options?"

parts.text: I'm looking to book an appointment, what's your availability?
Do you have any openings for an appointment?
What are your available appointment slots?
I need an appointment for my screens
What times do you have open?
I want to book an appointment

variants.text: How many screens do you need serviced?
Sorry, I didn't catch that. How many screens do you need serviced? Please reply with a number like 3 or 4.
What day works best for your appointment?
Awesome! I'll block that time off for you next. (This feature coming soon!)
Great! Let me check real-time availability for your $session.params.screens_needed screens on $session.params.appointment_date.

text: Great! Let’s finish up with a few quick details.
Awesome! Let’s grab your contact info to lock in the appointment.
Thanks! What’s the best phone number to reach you at?
If you'd like, share your email (or say 'skip').
No problem! Just to confirm, is $session.params.user_phone a mobile number that can receive text messages?
